      <title>中国在加拿大农场出口上有征税的农作物市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/canola-falls-by-exchange-limit-as-china-sets-tariffs-on-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周末对加拿大菜籽产品征收关税的举动已为作物跌落的价格，增加了更多的不确定性，这对一系列贸易战的全球粮食流动增加了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/canola-falls-by-exchange-limit-as-china-sets-tariffs-on-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 00:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着经济恐惧刺激飞往债券的飞行：市场包裹，股票下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球最大经济体的关税和政府解雇会在全球市场上延长三周的波动性。随着华尔街的预报措施调整看涨的看法，美国的股票下跌，而对经济衰退的需求促进了美国和欧洲的主权债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Mar 2025 21:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
